fields.name: MaxPercentUnhealthyPartitionsPerService
fields.description: The maximum percentage of partitions per service allowed to be unhealthy before your application is considered in error.

fields.name: MaxPercentUnhealthyReplicasPerPartition
fields.description: The maximum percentage of replicas per partition allowed to be unhealthy before your application is considered in error.

fields.name: MaxPercentUnhealthyServices
fields.description: The maximum percentage of services allowed to be unhealthy before your application is considered in error.
